{"tid":2257140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本防衛大臣指中國在疫情下加速擴大軍事影響力","createTime":"2020-10-25T02:47:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T03:18:41.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"163c1977b3ee0ca934ff413d118d52e8473a31a7","tid":2257140,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T02:47:42.000Z","msg":"日本防衛大臣指中國在疫情下加速擴大軍事影響力<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556514-20201024.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556514-20201024.htm&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=59c706a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556514-20201024.htm&h=dc2f5969\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556514-20201024.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n日本防衛大臣岸信夫批評中國在新型冠狀病毒疫情下，仍然在東海及南海等，加速擴大軍事影響力，試圖單方面改變現狀。<br />\n<br />\n共同社報道，岸信夫在日美合作相關國際會議上發表視像講話，指出中國海警船駛入尖閣諸島，即是中方稱的釣魚島附近海域，長時間停留，並在南海興建人工島。他又說，中國過去30年的國防費用上升約40倍，認為在欠缺透明度的情況下，中國迅速增強軍事實力的質和量，令他擔憂，日本將與美國等國家，加強安全保障領域的合作。<br />\n<br />\n首相菅義偉亦透過視像發言，表示今後將繼續強化日美同盟的作用和能力，亦會加強與澳洲等國的合作。"},{"pid":"f9edb171a4d535ef742b6edd23b18e8e07d16582","tid":2257140,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T02:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/commentaries/wp/COM-10252017065035.html/com1025.png/@@images/336de8ba-d371-42a3-b6ef-3d6aa6a0b384.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fcommentaries%2Fwp%2FCOM-10252017065035.html%2Fcom1025.png%2F%40%40images%2F336de8ba-d371-42a3-b6ef-3d6aa6a0b384.png&h=6845981e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d741f2c0337f5f139be1013bf27d72a04b09ee11","tid":2257140,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T02:54:17.000Z","msg":"如果拜登做埋總統，成個亞洲一定比中國食左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c54225f42ad8566f41645f8d08681a2609f74cd","tid":2257140,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T03:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50a727ef9c564df7731e256494f734813dc4792","tid":2257140,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T03:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WbQz49b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWbQz49b.gif&h=da12d4c1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}